me. This pilot programme took place in Antigua January 2018. \u00a0Can&#8217;t wait for the next phase in Summer 2018.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1522\" src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/K5zvVeIuuTujEU8ye8Yvjn0ZJnzbDL7L28dRh3PsqnW5Hpp6CmDJ-W_kZHW6wh1NIb3cG738qkfhMB4hL-9J1-f5Otur4-N6fG6JndrERA=s300\" alt=\"GirlsCanCode\" width=\"138\" height=\"181\" \/><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1524\" src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/p-XC4ThYVS5n-BjqB-PxZHEBGW5zBFr19MxCNVbEk3L0IncHCdLMsVaDPpKPHlZln0AslI7aXg1qh5LVGH3Nv_0_eOGg8CISvV-henwoOk0=s300\" alt=\"Wrap up at teen Dadlihack\" width=\"237\" height=\"182\" \/><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1523\" src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/FVffHwK7f2z4lY3RCuz_4OaVzDhQA8-4OU3IGpIuqfPEsqvNWoQ2ADBrA8-XmPpXQaRdZrHQNtQade0Ei46Ie6EL7fRiVjgiDX7CrDSY6Ls=s300\" alt=\"Sonic-Pi\" width=\"181\" height=\"181\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"mceTemp\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As part of OceanGeneration #dadlihack weekend looking at how technology can help with disaster preparedness and relief. Working on behalf of FireTechCamp to run teen computer science workshops for schools in Antigua. It was an amazing experience for everyone involved.&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[52,64,46,54],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1520"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1520"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/www.ready